cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.PF, cs.MA. 

This paper deals with the peak age-of-information (PAoI) in a queueing system with packet delivery error, which is a common problem in networked systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves information theory and communication theory, which suggests cs.IT (Information Theory) as another likely category. The use of policies to manage the queueing system and minimize PAoI indicates cs.SY (Systems and Control) as a possible category. The paper also involves mathematical analysis and modeling, which suggests cs.PF (Performance) and cs.MA (Mathematical Analysis) as additional possible categories.
